text: The second inauguration of Barack Obama as President of the United States was held privately on this date January 20 in 2013 in the Blue Room of the White House. His second inauguration was held publicly the next day on January 21. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zncqb-n3zMo&index=21&list=PLO7bQPaBH-JTbes6jItFif-w8d4mGomnK …
